      <body>Btw, in rails 3 I18n.reload! is called twice on initialization in railtie.rb, namely in &quot;i18n.initialize&quot; and in the after_initialize. Not sure if any of the two could be removed.. it seems to me the call in the initialize block could be removed. What do you think?</body>
