      <body>In development mode I do want to reload the classes on each request, just not all the i18n stuff, so delegating to cache_caches is not what I want.

I think &gt; 90% don't do i18n, they just hard code all strings. So having i18n reload by default is just a waste for them.</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;In development mode I do want to reload the classes on each
request, just not all the i18n stuff, so delegating to cache_caches
is not what I want.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I think &amp;gt; 90% don't do i18n, they just hard code all strings.
So having i18n reload by default is just a waste for them.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
